Vim Notes:

copy line - y(twice)
copy word -yw
copy textblock - 
[select text in visual mode ...go insert mode then hit y...then p]

paste - p

modes change - ctrl+[

navigation:
basic - hjkl
page top - gg
page bottom - G

next blank line - shift [ or ]

code folding:
toggle - za
everything - zM
unfold - zR

indent:
(after selecting block of text in visual mode)
shift + < or >

adjust indents:
select a block hit =
or
gg=G
